Class QueuedEdition

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.pso.workflow.QueuedEdition
Deprecated. use the IPSRxPublisherService classes directly instead. 

public class QueuedEdition
extends java.lang.Object

A Data Object describing an edition to be run in the future. As of 6.6, this is no longer needed. It is kept for compatibility purposes only.
